Bounty Contracts

	Philosophy

		-
			Bounty contracts are open contracts that any external entity may undertake, with such
			contracts being fulfilled and compensated on a first-come first-serve basis.
		-

	Principles

		Bounty Board

			-
				A bounty board is a list of open contracts.
			-

		Reverse Contract

			-
				A reverse contract is a contract proposed to the contractee by the contractor.
			-